      "Run _DAILY\\0H_CONTRACT_FILL_RECONCILE.bat to rebuild execution-quality reconciliation.",
      "Run _DAILY\\0I_CONTRACT_EXIT_INTENT_BACKFILL.bat, then _DAILY\\0J_CONTRACT_EXIT_RECONCILE.bat."
    ]
  }
